  <h2 class="section-title">From <span>cathode</span><br/>to finished reel.</h2>
  <div class="process-timeline">
    <div class="process-track"></div>
    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="ps-node">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect x="3" y="8" width="16" height="10" rx="1" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="1.3"/>
          <path d="M7 8V6a4 4 0 018 0v2" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="1.3"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ps-title">Copper Cathode Receipt</div>
      <div class="ps-body">Grade A copper cathode (≥99.97% Cu) received, sampled, and batch-recorded against supplier certificate.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="ps-node">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="1.3"/>
          <path d="M11 4v14M4 11h14" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="0.9"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ps-title">Casting & Rolling</div>
      <div class="ps-body">Cathode melted, continuously cast, and hot-rolled into 8mm copper rod. OF variants processed under inert atmosphere.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="ps-node">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M4 11 Q8 5 11 11 Q14 17 18 11" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none"/>
          <circle cx="4" cy="11" r="1.5" fill="#E02020"/>
          <circle cx="18" cy="11" r="1.5" fill="#E02020"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ps-title">Wire Drawing</div>
      <div class="ps-body">48 lines reduce rod 8mm → 0.05mm with inline annealing to restore ductility and conductivity throughout.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="ps-node">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect x="3" y="5" width="16" height="12" rx="1.5" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="1.3"/>
          <line x1="3" y1="11" x2="19" y2="11" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="0.8"/>
          <line x1="9" y1="5" x2="9" y2="17" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="0.8"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ps-title">Stranding & Insulation</div>
      <div class="ps-body">Wires stranded to spec, then insulated with PVC, XLPE, LSZH, or enamel per product type and application.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="ps-node">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M5 12l4 4 8-8" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8" stroke="#E02020" stroke-width="1"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ps-title">QC & Dispatch</div>
      <div class="ps-body">100% electrical & spark testing, dimensional checks, certificate issue. Full batch traceability. 48hr despatch.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

